<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Aachal ❤️</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Segoe UI,sans-serif}
body{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff758c,#ff7eb3);color:white;text-align:center;overflow-x:hidden}
section{padding:70px 20px}
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center}
h1{font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:15px}
.card{max-width:800px;margin:15px auto;padding:20px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.btn{padding:14px 28px;border:none;border-radius:30px;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:20px}
.heart{position:fixed;animation:float 5s linear infinite}
@keyframes float{
from{transform:translateY(100vh)}
to{transform:translateY(-100px)}
}
#letter,#surprise{display:none}
footer{padding:30px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
<h1>🎂 Happy Birthday Aachal ❤️</h1>
<h2>From Ritesh</h2>

<div class="card">
<p>
Today is all about celebrating you. ❤️<br><br>
I hope your day is filled with happiness, laughter, beautiful memories and everything you wish for.
Thank you for being part of my life and making it brighter.
</p>
</div>

<button class="btn" onclick="showLetter()">Open Secret Message mt kr meri jaan 💌</button>
</section>

<section>
<h1>✨ Our Story ✨</h1>
<div class="card">
We met at a wedding, and who knew that one meeting would become something so special?
Then came Snapchat conversations, late chats, smiles, memories, and moments that I never want to forget par 2nd call huaa tha sayd na . ❤️
</div>
</section>

<section>
<h1>📸 My Favorite Memory</h1>
<div class="card">
One of my favorite memories is when you secretly took my photos and videos.
Every time I think about it, it makes me smile ha pr isko chor bolt hai zero civic sence. 🥰
</div>
</section>

<section>
<h1>💖 Why I Like You 💖</h1>

<div class="card">
I have a lot of reasons to like you, but if I started writing all of them,
this website would never end. ❤️

So here are just 10 reasons that instantly come to my mind...
</div>

<div class="card">😊 Your smile can make my day better.</div>
<div class="card">💬 Talking to you never feels boring.</div>
<div class="card">✨ You came into my life unexpectedly and made it special.</div>
<div class="card">📸 The memory of you secretly taking my photos.</div>
<div class="card">🥰 You make ordinary moments memorable.</div>
<div class="card">❤️ You always stay on my mind.</div>
<div class="card">🌹 You make me smile without trying.</div>
<div class="card">💖 Every conversation feels special.</div>
<div class="card">🫶 You are one of my favorite people.</div>
<div class="card">💕 Because you're simply Aachal.</div>
<div class="card"> pr sun ye faguniya hm tumko itta chahate hai itta chahata hai kya bataye kitta chahate hai .</div>
</section>

<section id="letter">
<h1>💌 Secret Message</h1>
<div class="card">
<h2>Dear Aachal ❤️</h2>
<br>
<p>
Happy Birthday, Angry Bird. 🐦❤️<br><br>

I may not know everything about you yet, but I know enough to appreciate how special you are.
Thank you for all the smiles, conversations and memories.

I hope this birthday brings you happiness, success, peace and countless reasons to smile.

And if there is one thing I want you to remember today, it's this:
You are appreciated more than you know. ❤️

<br><br>
Happy Birthday, Mrs. Serious. 🎂✨
<br><br>
— Ritesh
</p>
</div>

<button class="btn" onclick="showSurprise()">Final Surprise 🎁</button>
</section>

<section id="surprise">
<h1>🎁 One Last Surprise</h1>
<div class="card">
If I had 100 wishes today, every single one would be for your happiness. ❤️<br><br>

May your smile never fade.<br>
May your dreams come true.<br>
May this year be your best one yet.<br><br>

Thank you for being part of my story.
<br><br>
Happy Birthday my angry bird ❤️
</div>
</section>

<footer>
Made with ❤️ by Ritesh babu yrr ek jagah spelling mistek ho gai hai dekh lena mujhe nh mil rh 
  
</footer>

<script>
function showLetter(){
document.getElementById('letter').style.display='block';
document.getElementById('letter').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});
}
function showSurprise(){
document.getElementById('surprise').style.display='block';
document.getElementById('surprise').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});
}
setInterval(()=>{
let h=document.createElement('div');
h.className='heart';
h.innerHTML='❤️';
h.style.left=Math.random()*100+'vw';
h.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*25)+'px';
document.body.appendChild(h);
setTimeout(()=>h.remove(),5000);
},300);
</script>

</body>
</html>
